<para style="p">A song; a psalm of the sons of Korah.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Great is Yahweh and greatly to be praised,</para>

<para style="q1">in the city of our God on his holy mountain.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Beautiful in elevation, the joy of the whole earth,</para>

<para style="q1">is Mount Zion, on the sides of the north,</para>

<para style="q1">the city of the great King.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />God has made himself known in her palaces as a refuge.</para>
